    public static class FoDAuthenticatingRestConnection.FoDAuthenticatingRestConnectionBuilder
extends FoDRestConnectionConfig<FoDAuthenticatingRestConnection.FoDAuthenticatingRestConnectionBuilder>
implements IRestConnectionBuilder<FoDAuthenticatingRestConnection>
    This class provides a builder pattern for configuring an FoDAuthenticatingRestConnection instance. It re-uses builder functionality from FoDRestConnectionConfig, and adds a build() method to build an FoDAuthenticatingRestConnection instance.
